invalid type: string "Graphs and Charts for Business Data\n121\n7.\nDoughnut charts:\na. Contains more than one data series.\nb. Comparable with Pie chart.\nc. Both a and b.\nd. None of the above.\n8.\nThe 2D graph using _______ , _________ axes and in 3D graph ______ axis is\nalso used.\na. Category, value, vertical.\nb. Horizontal, vertical, depth.\nc. Category, value, series.\nd.\nb and c both.